title: Transferring from a Pixel 4 to a Pixel 5. The Pixel 4 says it does not accept this accessory
content:
Setting up a Pixel 5, transferring from a Pixel 4.
Followed the steps on the Pixel 5 and got to "Phones are connected".
The Pixel 4 gave a message, I can't remember the exact words, saying the apps on this phone do not support the device connected.
No further  progress.
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 5
